==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Turko-Iranian
<hw>Tur`ko-I*ra"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>pr. a.</pos>
<fld>(Ethnol.)</fld> <def>Designating, or pert. to, a mixed racial type
including the Afghans, and characterized chiefly by stature above mean,
fair complexion, dark, or sometimes gray, eyes, brachycephaly, and very
long, prominent, and moderately narrow nose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Turko-Iranian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Turko-Iranian
<hw>Tur`ko-I*ra"ni*an</hw>, <pos>pr. n.</pos> <def>A member of any race
of the Turko-Iranian type.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Turkois</ent>⟦br⟧
